# Equal

classDiagram
    Equal <|-- Hash
    Equal <|-- Ord
    class Equal {
      Chunk[A: Equal]
      F[A: Equal]: DeriveEqual
      Either[A: Equal, B: Equal]
      Exit[E: Equal, A: Equal]
      List[A: Equal]
      Map[A, B: Equal]
      NonEmptyChunk[A: Equal]
      Option[A: Equal]
      Try[A: Equal]
      ⟮A: Equal, ..., Z: Equal⟯
      Vector[A: Equal]
    }
